The iot project contains:
  - .gitignore: the file that specifies which files and directories to ignore in git
  - .pio: the directory that contains the PlatformIO build files
  - .vscode: the directory that contains the Visual Studio Code configuration files
  - include: the header files for the project
  - platformio.ini: the configuration file for PlatformIO
  - README: this file
  - sdkconfig: the file that contains the SDK configuration for the project
  - src: the main source code of the project
  - test: This directory is intended for PlatformIO Test Runner and project tests.
  - lib: This directory is intended for project specific (private) libraries.
